   <h1>The Troll&#39;s Bane Chronicle</h1>

   <h2>The fifth year of the new era: December</h2>

<p>In year five of the new age, on the 2nd December, Kevin Lightdot asks the people of Gobiath to plant more cherry trees. It seems, that the many carpenters make it impossible for the trees to grow.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 2nd December, Alysha meets a 8 year old boy named Angor Firgus. His mother Ashley is missing, and the people search for hints on her remain.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 2nd December, Kevin Lightdot warns the people of Greenbriar because of a giant spider that was seen on the halfling island and that attacked a friend of Kevin.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 2nd December a dead body is found. It was bound to a tree near the Grey Refuge, and was later identified as Nymus Nottenfid.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 2nd December Konsteric Kamren is asking about the ownership of the territory around the oasis. A angry discussion between Varshikar and Silverbrand broke loose about who of both owns the oasis.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 3rd December, Gashlak Bonebreaker reports about an attack on his person by Alexander von Hattingen, a member of the Grey Rose. Alexander himself states the incident from his point of view, and the orc is losing his believability.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 3rd December, Kevin Lightdot asks for help against the demons and skeletons that have overrun the mummy temple.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 4th December, the dwarven mastersmith Graubart leaves the town of the dwarves, Silverbrand. His place is took by a dwarf named Garabosch.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 5th December, the dwarf Lord Balren Goldsmith founds a neutral Clan, named Bal-Kha'zard. All races shall unite under him and have fun by simply living. After a short time, the clan was disbanded again.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 8th December another dead body is found next to the Grey Refuge. This time, the person was identified as Saradomin Meranwyn.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 8th December, a new guild is found, named "The Paien". This guild was to protect all flowers and trees, including all natural things.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 9th December, the Librarian and Elder of the Grey Light, Sir Jeron Giandor asks the people to protect the graveyard against any form of vandalism. His opinion was because he spoke to a king of the undead, however, the people did not belief that this would bring any piece onto Gobiath.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 11th December, Kamik Windslasher and Devrah Windslasher (Liioness) marry each other. Because of the bad situation of Gobiath, the ceremony was held in private. They announced to make a bigger festival, when the situation was more calm again.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 11th December, Culandria announces the death of the first paladin of Kallahorn. His name was Sylathen.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 11th December, the earl of the Grey Rose, Lennier, asks the dwarves of Silverbrand to fight for their fallen city. The traitor Gishmel and the thieves Arameh and Jacob, aswell as some orcs around Alkuurg attacked the town and won.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 12th December, Lutup Kraknay asks the people in public why someone tries to kill his Goshna Drumbeater and her husband.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 12th December, the children Mairead and Rhiannon Fayed announce their marriage. They said, that they marry because they did not like moshrooms, but perhaps those brats have eaten poisonous mushrooms themself.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 12th of December, King Tialdin announces the new king of Silverbrand to be Duncan Orloff. Also, he announces how Silverbrand will be lead in the future.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 12th December, the carpenter Aenur is attacked in the forest by Bulbsponge fairies with poison gas. The day before he was talking to nice Toadstool fairies.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 16th December, Gabon Corad, leader of the Shadow Horde announces that he is going to duel Ghorn Gemfist. Gabon did not wanted to move back in conflict to Alkuurg and the dwarf Gishmel who wanted to sell Silverbrand.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 18th December, Misjilah Mehialho announces herself queen of Tol Vanima. She says, it would be better for her race.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 18th December, Moatha does a poll to the elves of Vanima and Gobiath about if they would like to be lead by Elders of a Queen.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 18th December, a new voting on the Elders of Tol Vanima is started.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 18th December, Gishmel is attacked by an army from Troll's Bane. He surrenders.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 19th December, Pendar Fayed asks for a meeting in the tavern of Trollsbane where everyone is invited. A new danger is to threaten the island, he says.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 24th December, Stephen Rothman, first Knight of Kallahorn, asks to speak the captain of the town guard in public.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 26th December, Derek Corydon asks for a brewer who could brew the beer and wine for a comming festival.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 26th December, Samantha Solay, selfproclaimed Archmage is searching for new students. Archmage Vasco Armengol Seda and Saladin Tyrus tell her, that she holds no magical power, but she is free to learn magic in the Magic Academy. Shortly after this, the imposter leaves and is never seen again.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 27th of December, Pendar Fayed announces that he is leaving the position as captain of the town guard. His new captain is Derek Corydon.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 28th of December, Stephen Rothman announces that the dwarf Gishmel ran away from the prison. After this, Alexander von Hattingen, has seen Gishmel, but was not able to catch him. Later that evening, Gishmel was caught and brought back into jail.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, on the 29th of December, the town was attacked by Skeletons, Beholders and Lichs. The attack could be defended.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new age, the dwarves of Silverbrand execute the dwarf Gishmel.</p>

